{"tid":2400900,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前年11月中環和你Lunch 7男2女今早被捕 下周四東區法院提堂","createTime":"2021-02-09T10:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T14:14:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59c2a1b37a5c7e9abf0da81cdb0fd42ffb333824","tid":2400900,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"2019年11月13日，中環上班一族在中午時分發起「和你Lunch」行動，抗議警方於中大圍城事件中的濫暴手法，最後釀成激烈警民衝突。事隔超過一年，警方港島總區重案組今日在全港各區拘捕並檢控7男2女，下周四（18日）提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，港島總區重案組當日事發後接手案件，經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日上午約7時在全港多區拘捕7名本地男子及2名本地女子，年齡介乎20至39歲。<br />\n<br />\n控罪方面，其中7名被捕人已各被控以一項「非法集結」罪，當中3人同時被控以一項「刑事毀壞」罪或「管有任何物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產」罪；另外2名被捕人則被控以一項「管有任何物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產」罪，案件將於2月18日下午在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210209/VSFBULZIMFBCLBCEP2YWWHDLBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210209%2FVSFBULZIMFBCLBCEP2YWWHDLBA%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNML32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=ce74f235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210209%2FVSFBULZIMFBCLBCEP2YWWHDLBA%2F&h=e418ca75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210209/VSFBULZIMFBCLBCEP2YWWHDLBA/</a>"},{"pid":"42dba789ac23637cfd7d7413e40fa7aad99336b3","tid":2400900,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c560127ba1c9547008e95cc3da7db5b68f55406d","tid":2400900,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as